---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import LegalsStructure from '../components/LegalsStructure.astro';
import SectionStructure from '../components/SectionStructure.astro';
import NavbarDesktop from '../components/header/NavbarDesktop.astro';
import NavbarMobile from '../components/header/NavbarMobile.astro';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
  <NavbarMobile isLanding={false} />

  <NavbarDesktop isLanding={false} />
  <main class="flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-10 lg:gap-12 xl:gap-16 bg-main">
    <LegalsStructure idSection="legals">
      <div class="flex justify-center items-center min-h-[400px] md:min-h-[550px] lg:min-h-[400px] xl:h-[550px]">
        <h2 class="font-bold font-Inter text-[24px]/[38px] text-wrap md:text-[48px] text-center border text-white border-red w-max py-3 px-4 rounded-full self-center lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl">
          Privacy Policy
        </h2>
      </div>
    </LegalsStructure>

    <SectionStructure idSection="legal-content">
      <article class="flex flex-col gap-5 pb-10">
        <div class="text-white flex flex-col gap-2 font-Inter bg-main w-full">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold lg:text-xl">Our Commitment to Your Privacy</h4>
          <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-base">
            At PrestigeSlotArena.com, your privacy is paramount. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you interact with our website.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-white flex flex-col gap-2 font-Inter bg-main w-full">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold lg:text-xl">1. Data We Collect</h4>
          <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-base">
            By using our site, we collect certain information to provide you with the best possible experience. This includes your contact details (name, email address, phone number), booking
            information (tournament dates), and payment details. We may also collect information about your interactions with our platform, such as pages visited and services of your interest.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-white flex flex-col gap-2 font-Inter bg-main w-full">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold lg:text-xl">2. How We Manage Your Information</h4>
          <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-base">
            The information we collect is used primarily to facilitate your bookings and ensure you have a seamless experience on our website. This includes processing payments, confirming
            reservations, and contacting you in regards to your booking. We may also use your data to improve our services, customize your experience, and promote special events that may be of your
            interest.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-white flex flex-col gap-2 font-Inter bg-main w-full">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold lg:text-xl">3. Data Sharing and Security</h4>
          <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-base">
            Your data is shared only with the events you book with and is protected with advanced encryption methods. We do not share or sell your personal information with third parties for marketing
            purposes. All transactions and personal data are handled safely to prevent unauthorized access.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-white flex flex-col gap-2 font-Inter bg-main w-full">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold lg:text-xl">4. Your Rights</h4>
          <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-base">
            You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information at any time. If you would like to request the removal of your information or update your details, please contact
            our support team. We are committed to complying with all applicable data protection laws and respecting your privacy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-white flex flex-col gap-2 font-Inter bg-main w-full">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold lg:text-xl">5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h4>
          <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-base">
            Our site uses cookies to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies allow us to remember your preferences and track your activity on our website to provide personalized options and
            suggestions. You can manage your cookie preferences from your browser settings.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-white flex flex-col gap-2 font-Inter bg-main w-full">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold lg:text-xl">6. Third-Party Service Providers</h4>
          <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-base">
            We might engage reliable third-party service providers to perform certain functions on our behalf, such as hosting our website, processing payments, and analyzing data. These providers
            have access to personal information required to perform their functions but are contractually enforced to protect your data and use it exclusively for the purposes we specify.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-white flex flex-col gap-2 font-Inter bg-main w-full">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold lg:text-xl">7. International Data Transfers</h4>
          <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-base">
            Your personal information may be transferred to and processed overseas, where data protection laws may vary. In such cases, we make sure that appropriate safeguards are in place to protect
            your information, in compliance with applicable laws.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-white flex flex-col gap-2 font-Inter bg-main w-full">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold lg:text-xl">8. Data Retention</h4>
          <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-base">
            We retain your personal data only as long as necessary to comply with the purposes outlined in this policy or as required by law. Once your information is no longer needed, we will make
            sure to erase or to anonymize it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-white flex flex-col gap-2 font-Inter bg-main w-full">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold lg:text-xl">9. Contacting Us</h4>
          <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-base">
            If you have any concerns or questions about this Privacy Policy or how your data is managed, please contact our customer support team. We are dedicated to addressing your concerns and
            ensuring that your privacy is well-protected.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-white flex flex-col gap-2 font-Inter bg-main w-full">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold lg:text-xl">10. Changes to This Policy</h4>
          <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-base">
            We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We encourage you to revisit this page periodically to keep up with any
            changes. Any updates to this policy will be effective immediately upon publishing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </SectionStructure>
  </main>
</Layout>
